{"tid":2297034,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"傑斯 : 誠蒙各位手足關心.  要暫時封咪, 但繼續堅持信念","createTime":"2020-11-23T03:42:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T07:19:03.000Z","uid":134071,"like":230,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"332a76f9b43e1709f19615032982d844c377c84f","tid":2297034,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T03:42:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/www.giggs.hk/posts/3403698516350484\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwww.giggs.hk%2Fposts%2F3403698516350484&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUnW5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=eaaa982e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/www.giggs.hk/posts/3403698516350484</a><br />\n<br />\n傑斯<br />\n35分鐘 &middot;<br />\n<br />\n誠蒙大家關心，本人及家人暫安好，不用擔心，謹此向大家報個平安。<br />\n過去兩天經歷，難以言喻，但幸好身邊有一班不離不棄的好友，陪著本人及家人，渡過難關，謹此衷心向你們説一聲：感激不盡，無以為報！<br />\n其他，因進入程序，就不便多言，敬請見諒。<br />\n一切來得突然，本人也需要一點時間，處理私人事務，唯有在此暫別咪前，暫別大家，雖不捨，但無奈！<br />\n過去兩天，最深刻的體會是，香港病得很重！<br />\n病的，像疫情，人與人之間只追求不被傳染，不被感染，那良知、公義呢？<br />\n有人會説，守法才是最重要，比良知、公義還要重要？甚至犧牲一切也在所不計？<br />\n我沒有答案，還在找尋守法之同時，良知不被埋沒，公義不被違背的一個良方，那怕今天這條良方，在香港，還存在與否，也嘗試繼續尋找吧。<br />\n臭格中，想到劉曉波，他説過，我沒有敵人⋯⋯<br />\n今天，雖此遭遇，但我也沒有敵人，只有香港人，誠希彼此互相反思，互相感染，讓這個家，早日康復！<br />\n講真話，行公義，好憐憫，還是我堅持的信念，但願我能感染身邊每一個人。<br />\n<br />\n傑斯<br />\n2020年11月23"},{"pid":"6b19603a6ede5234344656720709557eb6b8d94f","tid":2297034,"uid":134071,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T03:43:07.000Z","msg":"手足保重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201121/L5WJILYNJZADFP2FHKGSLN6QTI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201121%2FL5WJILYNJZADFP2FHKGSLN6QTI%2F&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUnW5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=cad40ed6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201121%2FL5WJILYNJZADFP2FHKGSLN6QTI%2F&h=ae5d6a4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201121/L5WJILYNJZADFP2FHKGSLN6QTI/</a>"},{"pid":"e9d964e74b91d94fa22e8fe55a52c9f452c8f035","tid":2297034,"uid":134071,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T03:43:43.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3413955d7f9abcb75965943e69ef5e0d30324a52","tid":2297034,"uid":284432,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T03:44:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8101a3b7c2c3830e41a94f30db93383a976f0d02","tid":2297034,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3413955d7f9abcb75965943e69ef5e0d30324a52","tid":2297034,"uid":284432,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T03:44:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T03:44:56.000Z","msg":"祝手足平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"684c4dbde0467198c49930347246baa3d1921216","tid":2297034,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T03:47:04.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0769e96a3b69a799c58a83f9e0dc6e4e2b44785","tid":2297034,"uid":28960,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T03:49:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2320a53cc772aaf1cd1f84e85925b203053c77d","tid":2297034,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e0769e96a3b69a799c58a83f9e0dc6e4e2b44785","tid":2297034,"uid":28960,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T03:49:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T03:51:29.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a